BESTCOM INFOTECH said unconsolidated sales
in June fell 4.10% to NT$890,418,000 from NT$928,507,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  6/2011           6/2010
Sales            890,418          928,507    
YOY%              -4.10%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           5,142,797        4,404,796   
YOY%              16.75% 
=================================================================
 